      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">52.241-4</ph> Change in Class of Service.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause" class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p " id="d3598e8">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="41.501.dita#FAR_41_501"
                     base="i1076423"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">41.501</xref>(c)(3)</ph>, insert a clause substantially the same as the following:</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" id="d3598e15">Change in Class of Service <ph outputclass="SmCaps" class="- topic/ph ">(Feb 1995)</ph>
         </p>
         <ol id="d3555e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3598e21">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            In the event of a change in the class of service, such service shall be provided at the Contractorâ€™s lowest available rate schedule applicable to the class of service furnished.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3598e26">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            Where the Contractor does not have on file with the regulatory body approved rate schedules applicable to services provided, no clause in this contract shall preclude the parties from negotiating a rate schedule applicable to the class of service furnished.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Endofclause">(End of clause)</p>
      </conbody>
